<div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p34318887-4.jpg" alt="Cuneiform writing on the back of a Lamassu in the University of Chicago Oriental Institute"><br><span class="pic-title">Cuneiform writing on the back of a Lamassu in the University of Chicago Oriental Institute</span></div>
<div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p34318887-5.jpg" alt="Modern impression of Achaemenid cylinder seal, 5th century BCE. A winged solar disc legiti"><br><span class="pic-title">Modern impression of Achaemenid cylinder seal, 5th century BCE. A winged solar disc legiti</span></div>
<div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p34318887-6.jpg" alt="Assyrian Hall; Musée du Louvre. Brooklyn Museum Archives, Goodyear Archival Collection"><br><span class="pic-title">Assyrian Hall; Musée du Louvre. Brooklyn Museum Archives, Goodyear Archival Collection</span></div><div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div><div class="middle"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p34318887-7.jpg" alt="一说狮身的叫拉玛苏（Lamassu），牛身叫舍杜（Shedu）？"><br><span class="pic-title">一说狮身的叫拉玛苏（Lamassu），牛身叫舍杜（Shedu）？</span></div>
